comments.body: Consider doing a loop in this test so we test multiple cases in a single test run.

It's a little hard to clean the code in single test run. Because `numpy.diag` do not support multi-dimension tensor, we must extract the corresponding diagonal elements by hand, so I may think it's more clearer to unroll the test cases in this way.
